package org.apache.eagle.security.auditlog;

import com.typesafe.config.Config;
import org.apache.eagle.security.service.ISecurityDataEnrichServiceClient;
import org.apache.eagle.security.service.IPZoneEntity;
import org.apache.eagle.security.enrich.AbstractDataEnrichLCM;

import java.util.Collection;

/**
 * Since 8/16/16.
 */
public class IPZoneDataEnrichLCM extends AbstractDataEnrichLCM<IPZoneEntity, String> {
    public IPZoneDataEnrichLCM(Config config){
        super(config);
    }
<fim_suffix>    @Override
    protected Collection<IPZoneEntity> loadFromService(ISecurityDataEnrichServiceClient client) {
        return client.listIPZones();
    }

    @Override
    public String getCacheKey(IPZoneEntity entity) {
        return entity.getIphost();
    }
}<fim_middle>// function below has no smell
